Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:51.05,def2,.PLAYERB:.,0,0,0,,Let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:52.51,def2,.PLAYERC:.,0,0,0,,I'm not done yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:55.00,def2,.PLAYERD:.,0,0,0,,Let's do it, let's do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.56,0:01:57.51,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Fight ! Fight !
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:02:00.03,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Guys, give it all you've got !
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:01.51,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Fight ! Fight !
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:14.34,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,How is it ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:18.78,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,The effective temperature seems to be about 43 degrees(110F).
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:22.58,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,We first have to battle this heat before we play against Meiwa, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.05,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I'm going to change my undershirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:31.16,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Um, I'll go buy some sports drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:38.22,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,At this rate, you'll all be dehydrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:41.25,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:42.44,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,I'll get going !
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:44.06,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,She's full of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:46.49,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Here we go !
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:00.12,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,You're working hard in this heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:03.46,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Don't say things that are obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:05.90,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Just think about the\Npredicament we're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:12.90,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,The game against our school \Nis next week{one week from now}, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:14.86,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,What brought you here, anyway ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:17.90,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Your practice will be over soon, right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:21.12,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,We still have one full \Nhour before 2 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.70,def2,.PLAYERS:.,0,0,0,,Water, water...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:23.93,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Oh, the water is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:24.87,def2,.PLAYERS:.,0,0,0,,What ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:26.87,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,I'm going to the city pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:29.51,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Why don't we go swimming\N when you're done with practice ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:32.84,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Swimming pool ? \NYou should go with Hideo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:34.24,def2,.PLAYERS:.,0,0,0,,Swimming pool ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:36.51,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Of course Hide-chan is coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:41.50,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Noda, come with us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:43.15,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,He's not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:46.37,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,There are lots of girls \Nwith high-cut swimsuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.30,def2,.PLAYERA:.,0,0,0,,High-cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.25,def2,.PLAYERB:.,0,0,0,,Girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:55.65,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,You changed your mind, right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.30,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:02.17,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:04.18,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:08.60,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:11.67,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,What's no good ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:17.63,def2,.PLAYERA:.,0,0,0,,If we go to the pool now, we can see that girl in her swimsuit ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:20.00,def2,.PLAYERB:.,0,0,0,,Will she be wearing a \Nhigh-cut swimsuit, too ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:23.92,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Everyone's thinking about Hikari's swimsuit now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:27.31,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Well, this practice is useless, anyway.{after all.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:29.92,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:31.30,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Hm ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:35.50,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,They're going to the swimming pool together. Why would she invite intruders ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.00,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:42.20,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, you were \Noften invited to join their dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:45.00,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Hideo wasn't comfortable around girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:48.00,def2,..KUNIMI..,0,0,0,,Despite the fact that he asked me to introduce him to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:52.56,def2,..KUNIMI..,0,0,0,,...he didn't even speak a word when I first set those two up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.99,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,He'd only whisper in a quiet voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:58.45,def2,..KUNIMI..,0,0,0,,If I weren't there as an interpreter, they wouldn't have been able to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:03.00,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,It took almost a year for them to speak with each other by themselves, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:06.25,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,That's how advanced \Nhe was at that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:07.50,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,On the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:12.59,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,...we entered junior high while we were still kids, so we didn't think about boy-girl stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:15.97,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,In particular, I grew up slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:17.89,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,You were so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:20.56,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,You definitely looked like\Nan elementary school kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:21.60,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:27.88,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Bear with it. After all, you did become popular with girls in junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:33.00,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,On the Valentine's Day before graduation,{from junior high} you received more chocolates than Hideo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:38.36,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,It really went slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.06,def2,TACHIBANA:,0,0,0,,Are Hiro and the others coming ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:48.06,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,He didn't say. But there's no use practicing in this heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:53.67,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Right about now, he's probably griping as he heads home to get his swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.11,def2,TACHIBANA:,0,0,0,,Really ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:57.86,def2,.PLAYERS:.,0,0,0,,To the swimming pool !
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:03.60,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,But really, we finished junior high. \NThings shouldn't stay the way they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:09.00,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Well, it's all right. She probably asked us out so that we could take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:13.45,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,I'm going to show you the splendid butterfly style of a former swimming club member.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:16.30,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Did you know ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:19.30,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,The "butterfly style" takes its name from a butterfly, Mr. Mothra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:20.91,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Who're you calling Mothra ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.64,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,So I'll see you at the\N city swimming pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.21,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:31.90,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.10,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,It's taking her too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:04.73,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,We're leaving second\Nbase open for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:06.92,def2,..CHILD:..,0,0,0,,Big Brother Yanagi !
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:09.40,def2,.YANAGI:..,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:11.93,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,Great timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.65,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,Can you coach \Nthese kids for a bit ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:17.30,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,There'll be an inter-town match\N the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:25.20,def2,.YANAGI:..,0,0,0,,In any case, catching the ball in front of you is fundamental.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:28.25,def2,.YANAGI:..,0,0,0,,Use the resilience of your\N knees, and stay low.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:32.90,def2,.YANAGI:..,0,0,0,,Until you actually catch the ball, don't worry about the runner or think about the throw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:37.55,def2,.YANAGI:..,0,0,0,,It's easiest to catch when the\N ball is about to hit the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:39.19,def2,.YANAGI:..,0,0,0,,The next easiest is when \Nthe ball is on a short hop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:41.20,def2,.YANAGI:..,0,0,0,,And then when the ball\Nis at the top of a hop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:43.80,def2,.YANAGI:..,0,0,0,,Other than those, the ball often changes course, so be alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:47.00,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:52.81,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,Wow. You're as good as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:54.42,def2,...MAN:...,0,0,0,,You really are a \Nfine second baseman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:01.08,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}We're keeping second \Nbase open for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.55,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Noda !
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.00,def2,TACHIBANA:,0,0,0,,Where's Hiro ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.30,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,He's coming later !
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:32.60,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,She's late.\N I wonder what she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:38.02,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I doubt that's what it is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:48.76,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,...I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:51.80,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,...it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.00,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Kunimi !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:06.34,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,This way !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:12.51,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Koga, practice is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:15.32,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Oh, I messed up again ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.79,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Let's go back to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:22.00,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:25.20,def2,...BOY:...,0,0,0,,Wait, Haruka. Why don't\N you introduce me to him ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:27.35,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Who is he ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:32.70,def2,...BOY:...,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. \NI'm Haruka's ex-boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.51,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,That's a strange name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:38.49,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Who's my ex-boyfriend ? Don't say weird things !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:42.13,def2,...BOY:...,0,0,0,,When she was in the first year of junior high, I received a love letter from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:43.90,def2,...BOY:...,0,0,0,,So we went out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:46.95,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,It wasn't a love letter !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:49.40,def2,...BOY:...,0,0,0,,She's a jealous girl, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:54.70,def2,...BOY:...,0,0,0,,If I even had a brief chat with another girl, she'd get angry, and it would become trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.60,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,What's your point ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:06.13,def2,...BOY:...,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry. We didn't have a really deep relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.68,def2,...BOY:...,0,0,0,,Not that deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.40,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,You're not popular, are you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:18.98,def2,...BOY:...,0,0,0,,I'm not popular with girls ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:27.45,def2,...BOY:...,0,0,0,,Haruka, you should tell him how many love letters I received in junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:29.30,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,With guys, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:31.85,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I asked if you were\Nnot popular with guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:39.80,def2,...BOY:...,0,0,0,,What's the point of being\Npopular with such things ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.21,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:43.10,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Kunimi, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:46.23,def2,...BOY:...,0,0,0,,Are you really fine with that, Haruka ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:52.47,def2,...BOY:...,0,0,0,,You'll regret it. It's rare for \Nme to ask out a girl myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:56.12,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Next time you ask her out, you should get my permission first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:58.70,def2,...BOY:...,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want\Nto talk to me like that ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:02.09,def2,...BOY:...,0,0,0,,I know a lot of bad boys around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.90,def2,.BADBOYA:.,0,0,0,,Hey, if isn't Hiro !
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:08.24,def2,.BADBOYA:.,0,0,0,,Long time no see. \NI heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:11.24,def2,.BADBOYA:.,0,0,0,,Your elbow wasn't \Nbroken after all, huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:13.60,def2,.BADBOYA:.,0,0,0,,I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:14.60,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.55,def2,.BADBOYA:.,0,0,0,,Are you in trouble or something ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:21.47,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Not really. I bought too \Nmany drinks, so I'm in a bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:24.05,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,And this guy says he doesn't want one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.25,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Can you drink some ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:28.10,def2,.BADBOYA:.,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:30.60,def2,.BADBOYA:.,0,0,0,,If you're in any trouble,\Njust let us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:32.60,def2,.BADBOYA:.,0,0,0,,I'll lend you a hand any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.47,0:11:34.12,def2,.BADBOYA:.,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:39.88,def2,.BADBOYB:.,0,0,0,,Get out of the way !
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:47.50,def2,...BOY:...,0,0,0,,Your girl is waiting for you. You should go to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:53.60,def2,...BOY:...,0,0,0,,Have a nice trip !
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.20,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:03.23,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,If you like, would you like to\Ngo eat some curry and rice ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:04.60,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.50,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,I know a great curry restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:09.50,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:12.06,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,If you have other \Nthings to do, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:15.55,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Well, we have to go\N back{to the school} before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:16.84,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,We left our bags there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.47,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.90,def2,TACHIBANA:,0,0,0,,You're not going to\Nswim anymore, Hikari ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.67,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,It's getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:42.70,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,In the end, he didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:46.44,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,I guess things have\Nchanged since junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:54.02,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,I was sure it was\Nsomewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:56.20,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Is there actually a restaurant\Nin a residential area like this ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:13:01.80,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Good restaurants are often\N found in unexpected places.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.67,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Oh, I know ! \NIt's in this alley !
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:09.72,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I don't mind if we\Ngo some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:12.11,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,No. Definitely no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:15.30,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:18.30,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,You don't have to be so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:22.00,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,No, I really want you to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:23.70,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Right, it must be past the station !
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.70,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Honestly, you really saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:31.11,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,That person won't take me seriously, no matter how many times I say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:33.40,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,He's unbelievably conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.35,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fscx155\fscy140\pos(325.786,127.111)} {\c&H8B8CD4&\3c&H33322D&}Shop Conceited
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:35.35,Karaoke Translation op,Comment,0,0,0,,{\a5\c&H33322D&\3c&HDEDEE5&\pos(508.261,278.222)}Original \NTriumphant \NFace
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:39.43,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,And who sent a love\Nletter to a guy like that ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:43.89,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,As I said, it wasn't \Nanything like a love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:46.80,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,It was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:47.40,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,It was just...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:58.11,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,More like I wrote something saying that I wanted to be a friend of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:09.31,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,That's kind of how it\Nis at that age, right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:10.37,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,How so ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:19.25,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,In the first year of junior high, girls just create idealistic fantasies from how someone looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:23.00,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,...and falls in love with love,\Nrather than with the boy himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:26.41,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Oh, is that how it is ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:31.45,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Tachibana is cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:34.64,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}Tachibana is a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:40.00,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Maybe I don't have much\Nluck with the lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:45.65,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,All the guys I thought could be\Nnice have mostly been misses...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.53,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,...when I look back and \Nwith a calmer mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:01.29,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,You should change this\N careless aspect of yours first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:04.49,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,You draw a "miss" because you hastily grab one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.49,0:15:05.48,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:10.74,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Hey, have you ever found a "hit" ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:14.90,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,In my case, there were\Nno more tickets left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:15.35,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,What ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:21.00,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I'll show you my junior high \Nphoto sometime. You'll laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:25.92,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Until the second year of junior high, I was a snot-nosed midget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:30.76,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Finally, my height caught up, and I started to think about maybe looking for a girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:33.81,def2,..KUNIMI..,0,0,0,,...but by then, girls that interested me were all in the midst of their first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:34.73,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Seriously ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:37.69,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,What's the point of lying about this sort of thing ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:42.34,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:43.64,def2,TACHIBANA:,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:47.31,def2,TACHIBANA:,0,0,0,,Well, do you want to get\Nsome tea or something ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:48.95,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.94,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,I want to take a \Nbath now, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:51.61,def2,TACHIBANA:,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:53.45,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:54.29,def2,TACHIBANA:,0,0,0,,Bye, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:01.20,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.99,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,On a second thought,\Nlet's have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:03.50,def2,TACHIBANA:,0,0,0,,Huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:05.30,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Okay ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:10.08,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,But you're popular with girls now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:10.76,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:15.19,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,I mean, you're definitely cool, \Nwhen you're pitching on the mound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:18.54,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I don't know if I should be happy to hear it from someone who tends to draw a miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.12,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:22.06,def2,TACHIBANA:,0,0,0,,Oh well, you're capricious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:24.60,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Now, never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:25.29,def2,TACHIBANA:,0,0,0,,Hm ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:28.72,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,What would you like to order ?\NIt's on me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:29.80,def2,TACHIBANA:,0,0,0,,Oh, lucky me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:40.20,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,So what would you like, Hide-chan ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:43.80,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,I'm convinced.\NIt's definitely this alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.99,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I've heard you say that so many times. My hunger is at its limit now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:50.96,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,I found it ! \NLook, this is the place !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:53.83,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Phew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:57.34,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,This one is a "hit."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:02.18,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Bottom of the ninth, a bases \Nloaded homerun for a walkoff win !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:03.00,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Right !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:20.82,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Hey, Kunimi !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:23.49,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Look ! They gave me this !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:26.53,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,She's having fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:40.03,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Oh, it's going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:44.11,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,It's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.29,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,It was pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:50.13,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.25,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I hope we'll get our second baseman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:10.05,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:15.92,def2,PRINCIPAL:,0,0,0,,What happened to your face ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:18.25,def2,.YANAGI:..,0,0,0,,Oh, I ran into a telephone pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:19.11,def2,PRINCIPAL:,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.24,def2,.YANAGI:..,0,0,0,,Dad, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:23.40,def2,PRINCIPAL:,0,0,0,,It was a good bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:28.10,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,I can go from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:29.69,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:33.32,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Before you draw a "hit,"\Ndon't get hit by a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:34.04,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:37.96,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I'll see you tomorrow, at the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:42.45,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Good night !\N Thanks for today !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:04.36,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,The fireworks were beautiful, Kunimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:16.10,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,What happened to you yesterday ?\NWe were waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:19.00,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,It's my life.\NI didn't say I'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:22.40,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:27.32,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,I was going to show you the \Nswimsuit figure of the grown-up Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:29.95,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,How are you grown up ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:33.34,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,The swimsuit itself is different from what I had in junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:36.39,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,It's a high-cut lewd\Nkind of swimsuit.{one with\Nthis kind of high-cut.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:37.89,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:41.44,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Even if you say so, you \Nactually regret it, don't you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:42.30,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Yeah, right !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:45.25,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,I don't even need to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:51.25,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,With my talent, I can totally see you naked in my imagination, even when you're dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:54.22,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Really ? So what's the color of my underwear today ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.36,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Pink with a polka dot pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:05.40,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,That's what you're wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:10.03,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Stop talking rubbish.\NJust go to your practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:11.51,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:18.99,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Hiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:25.99,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,I'll cheer for you for now, until your club becomes official.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:30.85,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Can you break Hideo's arm \Nwhen you get a chance, then ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:36.10,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,You moron !\NGive me the apple back !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:37.88,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,It's in my stomach already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.66,0:20:40.85,def2,.HIKARI:..,0,0,0,,Geez. He really is still a brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:53.65,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Don't take unnecessary risks and charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:55.56,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,Make sure to keep\Nthe ball in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:59.00,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,You're going to throw, right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:00.94,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Is this okay ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:03.90,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:08.70,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}I mean, you're definitely cool, \Nwhen you're pitching on the mound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:15.91,def2,..NODA:...,0,0,0,,One more !
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:23.75,def2,..KINE:...,0,0,0,,Yahoo !
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:27.67,def2,..KINE:...,0,0,0,,There !
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:32.97,def2,..KINE:...,0,0,0,,{laughs} How about it, Kunimi ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:40.84,def2,..KINE:...,0,0,0,,Right now, I can settle for two\Ndates with Koga, including a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:43.60,def2,..KINE:...,0,0,0,,The price will definitely rise. If you're going to buy, now is the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:45.70,def2,..KINE:...,0,0,0,,For inquiry, contact the soccer club.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:51.49,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,Guys who approach \Nyou are all like that ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:53.00,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:57.55,def2,.HARUKA:..,0,0,0,,Even though I graduated from junior high, \Nmy luck with the draw hasn't changed, huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:03.66,def2,.KUNIMI:..,0,0,0,,In any case, one more \Nweek until the fateful game.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:16.80,Karaoke Translation op,..EDSONG:...,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,463.111)}If you have a hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:24.60,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(302.222,466.667)}...that I can hold forever as I walk.
