Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:40.32,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(324.444,466.667)}...rather than the footsteps that\N\N\N sound further and further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:43.92,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(311.111,468.444)}The star I'm watching today...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:48.40,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(315.556,464.889)}...glistened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:54.02,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,467.556)}In the town full of things that disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.33,0:22:58.15,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(314.667,465.778)}...I thought to myself, wishfully:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.55,0:23:06.13,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(314.667,467.556)}Let's return to "two of us," let's return together...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:14.25,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(315.556,469.333)}...rather than losing our time to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.43,0:23:17.65,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,464.889)}Happiness is not something...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:22.48,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(313.778,466.667)}...that someone does for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.78,0:23:31.05,Karaoke Translation op,....SONG....,0,0,0,,{\pos(324.444,467.556)}It means that I have someone I can embrace.
